{"tid":2375270,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"1月22日，一名內地男子和一名港人，均曾到過武漢，經高鐵抵港後，翌日確診","createTime":"2021-01-22T02:07:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T05:48:52.000Z","uid":90601,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"928e6f3950de19917570694fd18ab772c4cc7d21","tid":2375270,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T02:07:17.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">2020年1月20日</span>，武漢及湖北省確診個案急增及疫情擴散至廣東省及深圳市首次出現確診個案後[8]，香港政府始要求從武漢抵達香港的航班的乘客需要填寫健康申報表，<span class=\"xx-large\">但不包括高鐵抵達香港的乘客，</span><br />\n<br />\n兩宗個案分別是一名內地男子和一名港人，均曾到過武漢，抵港後1月22日被「高度懷疑」感染新冠病毒，翌日確診。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">1月22日，</span></span>因為高鐵乘客免填健康申報的漏招，令香港出現首兩宗初步確診從武漢乘高鐵返港的輸入個案，暴露出高鐵為防疫缺口，[12]港府才把填健康申報表擴展至乘高鐵返港的旅客[13]<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20201231/s00001/1608788477398/2020%E5%9B%9E%E9%A1%A7-%E7%96%AB%E6%88%B0%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4-%E5%9B%9E%E6%9C%9B%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E9%99%B0%E9%9C%BE%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF2020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20201231%2Fs00001%2F1608788477398%2F2020%25E5%259B%259E%25E9%25A1%25A7-%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2588%25B0%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%259C%259B%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E9%2599%25B0%25E9%259C%25BE%25E4%25B8%258B%25E7%259A%2584%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF2020&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TfjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=8681290d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20201231%2Fs00001%2F1608788477398%2F2020%25E5%259B%259E%25E9%25A1%25A7-%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2588%25B0%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%259C%259B%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E9%2599%25B0%25E9%259C%25BE%25E4%25B8%258B%25E7%259A%2584%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%